data.description: Beautiful 5 bdrm 2.5 baths historic two-story, 2862SF home! Built in 1907 & UPDATED! Boasts gorgeous hardwoods throughout, open floor plan, high ceilings, transom windows, 2 fireplaces, large bedrooms, jacuzzi tub, large front porch & enclosed balcony. Downstairs formal living & parlor, living room w/wood ceiling, tall base boards, all new carpets and paint throughout. 2 HVAC units. Gas stove, W&D, refrigerator remain. Located one block from elementary school & 6 blocks from high school!
